---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="八字研究所 | 免費線上八字排盤・AI 智能命理分析・四柱八字解析"
  description="傳承千年的東方命理智慧，結合現代 AI 科技，提供免費線上八字排盤與命理分析。輸入出生年月日時，即時獲得四柱八字命盤解讀。"
  activePage="home"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero/bagua-cosmos.webp" alt="" class="hero-bg-img" loading="eager" />
      <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
        <source src="/images/hero/divination-master.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <canvas class="hero-canvas" id="hero-canvas"></canvas>
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container hero-content">
      <span class="overline hero-overline">免費・即時排盤・AI 智慧解讀</span>
      <h1>四柱八字命理<br>解讀你的人生密碼</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">傳承千年的東方命理智慧，結合現代科技，為你提供即時、精準的八字排盤與命理分析。</p>

      <form class="hero-form" id="hero-form">
        <div class="hero-form-grid">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="hero-date">出生日期</label>
            <input type="date" id="hero-date" class="form-input" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="hero-hour">出生時辰</label>
            <select id="hero-hour" class="form-input" required>
              <option value="">請選擇時辰</option>
              <option value="0">子時 (23:00–01:00)</option>
              <option value="1">丑時 (01:00–03:00)</option>
              <option value="3">寅時 (03:00–05:00)</option>
              <option value="5">卯時 (05:00–07:00)</option>
              <option value="7">辰時 (07:00–09:00)</option>
              <option value="9">巳時 (09:00–11:00)</option>
              <option value="11">午時 (11:00–13:00)</option>
              <option value="13">未時 (13:00–15:00)</option>
              <option value="15">申時 (15:00–17:00)</option>
              <option value="17">酉時 (17:00–19:00)</option>
              <option value="19">戌時 (19:00–21:00)</option>
              <option value="21">亥時 (21:00–23:00)</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>性別</label>
            <div class="form-radio-group">
              <label><input type="radio" name="gender" value="male" checked /> 男</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="gender" value="female" /> 女</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg hero-submit">免費排盤</button>
      </form>

      <p class="hero-proof">已有超過 <strong>2,000</strong> 人使用</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Props -->
  <section class="section" id="value-props">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <span class="overline">為什麼選擇八字研究所</span>
        <h2>全方位的命理服務</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>即時排盤</h3>
          <p>輸入出生年月日時，一鍵完成四柱八字排盤，即時獲得完整命盤。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">🤖</div>
          <h3>AI 分析</h3>
          <p>結合人工智慧技術，根據你的命盤提供個人化的命理解讀與建議。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">🎁</div>
          <h3>完全免費</h3>
          <p>所有排盤工具與學習資源完全免費開放，無需註冊即可使用。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">📜</div>
          <h3>命理智慧</h3>
          <p>忠於傳統，提供完整的天干地支、五行、十神分析，深入理解命盤。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid fade-up" id="stats">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="2000">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">排盤次數</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="10">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">天干</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="12">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">地支</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="4.9" data-decimal="true">0</div>
